<p>Kylie - who has topped Forbes' list of youngest self-made billionaires for the past two years - bought the 15,350 square feet pad in April. </p>

<p>It's unclear if Kylie will be completely ditching her Hidden Hills digs, a neighborhood her family and friends have colonized throughout the years.</p>

<p>The social media sensation picked up her current property in 2016 for $12million.</p>

<p>The mansion sprawls over 13,200 square feet, according to real estate site Trulia.</p>

